Cell["\<\
The disjoint  diagrams at second order are 720 in total. These are \
distributed as follows:
i) 48 Bogoliubov diagrams dressed in the antidiagonal;
ii) 48 Bogoliubov diagrams dressed in the diagonal;
iii) 96 Bogoliubov diagrams dressed in both the diagonal and the antidiagonal;
iv) 48 Direct diagrams dressed in the left propagator;
v) 48 Direct diagrams dressed in the right propagator;
vi) 96 Direct diagrams dressed in both the left and the right propagator;
vii) 48 Exchange diagrams dressed in the propagator above;
viii) 48 Exchange diagrams dressed in the propagator below;
ix) 96 Exchange diagrams dressed in both the above and below propagator;\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8746447846491413`*^9, 3.874644822571206*^9}, {
   3.874644938314557*^9, 3.874644942272763*^9}, {3.8836802941172266`*^9, 
