\>", "Section",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8747474873699455`*^9, 3.8747475586269774`*^9}, {
  3.8836821843140464`*^9, 3.883682185030684*^9}, {3.8886425005080795`*^9, 
  3.8886425041635475`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"21f754e9-e7fa-44cc-9ec5-\
5bd7f34da51f"],

Cell["\<\
Direct diagrams with unperturbed 1-body propagator on the right are \
processed. Their initial number is 48 in total.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8836813753146152`*^9, 3.88368147043666*^9}, {
   3.8836820487185183`*^9, 3.88368205024879*^9}, {3.883682180609577*^9, 
   3.883682181425793*^9}, {3.8895326177197933`*^9, 3.8895326190004883`*^9}, {
   3.8927832371377015`*^9, 3.892783237556256*^9}, {3.911906600155179*^9, 
   3.911906604269761*^9}, {3.9123240718456955`*^9, 3.9123240720005255`*^9}, 
   3.9137836479808187`*^9},ExpressionUUID->"a875ff06-c3e3-445e-87ed-\
01f06136a565"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["\<\
Left-dressed disjoint direct diagrams with non-identical one-body vertices\
\>", "Subsection",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9123225301750393`*^9, 3.9123225545237913`*^9}, {
  3.9123286967354116`*^9, 
  3.9123287107977743`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"f80a4a74-b4b7-4228-92c3-\
12afd5c26fc6"],

Cell["\<\
Depending on the components of the one-body potential into play, symmetry \
rules may apply and reduce the total number of fully-contracted terms. When \
the multiplied Nambu components of the one-body potential are distinct, no \
vertex exchange is possible. Additionally, since single-particle index \
transpositions within each one-body vertex are forbidden, no filtration \
process is necessary. Thus, the number of inequivalent left-dressed disjoint \
direct contributions with non-identical vertices at second order remains \
equal to 48.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.912322579269453*^9, 3.9123226345921354`*^9}, {
   3.9123226697432995`*^9, 3.9123228694040194`*^9}, {3.912323377321495*^9, 
   3.9123233835289555`*^9}, {3.9123331180668077`*^9, 3.912333133784379*^9}, 
   3.9137836717019677`*^9},ExpressionUUID->"296e6c6a-be10-409f-92ab-\
e031e0bdeee4"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{"For", "[", 
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{"u", "=", "1"}], ",", 
    RowBox[{"u", "\[LessEqual]", "48"}], ",", 
    RowBox[{"u", "++"}], ",", 
    RowBox[{"Print", "[", 
     RowBox[{"\"\<CombDirLeft[[\>\"", ",", "u", ",", "\"\<]]=\>\"", ",", 
      RowBox[{"AdisjDirLeft", "[", 
       RowBox[{"[", "u", "]"}], "]"}], ",", "\"\<;\>\""}], "]"}]}], "]"}], 
  ";"}]], "Input",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8747489659683185`*^9, 3.874748971262155*^9}, {
   3.874750278096981*^9, 3.874750278551973*^9}, {3.8747509325127506`*^9, 
