Cell["\<\
There are only 8 inequivalent third-order right-dressed disjoint direct \
diagrams with three identical one-body vertices. The multiplicity check is \
fulfilled.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8895308415440407`*^9, 3.889530867561658*^9}, {
