Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["\<\
Disjoint direct diagrams with left-and-right-dressed single-particle \
propagators\
\>", "Section",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8747474873699455`*^9, 3.8747475345907583`*^9}, {
  3.8884847013485146`*^9, 3.888484713293386*^9}, {3.888642450412324*^9, 
  3.8886424579370823`*^9}, {3.911968252699196*^9, 
  3.9119682559798*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"7900b447-cb99-45fd-92d3-a2302c95b95d"],

Cell["\<\
Direct diagrams with perturbed 1-body propagators on the left and the right \
are processed. Their initial number is 96 in total.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8836813753146152`*^9, 3.88368147043666*^9}, {
  3.8836820487185183`*^9, 3.88368205024879*^9}, {3.883682180609577*^9, 
  3.883682181425793*^9}, {3.8895326177197933`*^9, 3.8895326190004883`*^9}, {
  3.8927832371377015`*^9, 3.892783237556256*^9}, {3.911906600155179*^9, 
  3.911906604269761*^9}, {3.912324076983011*^9, 3.912324077222091*^9}, {
  3.912328531280779*^9, 3.912328549293477*^9}, {3.913797272269909*^9, 
  3.9137972728545637`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"a24d12e7-541f-48bf-bed7-\
fd02a026bee9"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["\<\
Left-and-right-dressed disjoint direct diagrams with non-identical one-body \
vertices\
\>", "Subsection",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9123225301750393`*^9, 3.9123225545237913`*^9}, {
  3.9123286967354116`*^9, 3.9123287432225227`*^9}, {3.9123341321434407`*^9, 
  3.912334135400854*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"276d2d87-8007-4037-a24c-\
eb8c7c019511"],

Cell["\<\
Depending on the components of the one-body potential into play, symmetry \
rules may apply and reduce the total number of fully-contracted terms. When \
the multiplied Nambu components of the one-body potential are distinct, no \
vertex exchange is possible. Additionally, since single-particle index \
transpositions within each one-body vertex are forbidden, no filtration \
process is necessary. Thus, the number of inequivalent left-and-right-dressed \
disjoint direct contributions with three non-identical vertices at third \
order remains equal to 96.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.912322579269453*^9, 3.9123226345921354`*^9}, {
  3.9123226697432995`*^9, 3.9123228694040194`*^9}, {3.912323377321495*^9, 
  3.9123233835289555`*^9}, {3.9123331180668077`*^9, 3.912333133784379*^9}, {
  3.9123337248637705`*^9, 3.912333725851756*^9}, {3.9123341439163065`*^9, 
  3.912334145838047*^9}, {3.9137972776267824`*^9, 
  3.913797288012329*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"caaf6f70-507c-4a57-9f15-\
04e9b6f0d1dc"],

