Cell["\<\
There are only 48 inequivalent third-order left-and-right-dressed disjoint \
direct diagrams with two identical one-body vertices. The multiplicity check \
is fulfilled.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8895308415440407`*^9, 3.889530867561658*^9}, {
   3.8895323828156104`*^9, 3.8895323995676107`*^9}, {3.889533186766015*^9, 
