Cell["\<\
There are only 16 inequivalent third-order left-and-right-dressed disjoint \
direct diagrams with three identical one-body vertices. The multiplicity \
check is fulfilled.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8895308415440407`*^9, 3.889530867561658*^9}, {
