Cell["\<\
There are only 24 inequivalent second-order below-dressed disjoint exchange \
diagrams with identical one-body vertices. The multiplicity check is \
fulfilled.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8895308415440407`*^9, 3.889530867561658*^9}, {
