Cell["\<\
There are only 48 inequivalent second-order above-and-below-dressed disjoint \
exchange diagrams with identical one-body vertices. The multiplicity check is \
fulfilled.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8895308415440407`*^9, 3.889530867561658*^9}, {
