Cell["\<\
There are only 24 inequivalent third-order antidiagonally-dressed disjoint \
Bogoliubov diagrams with identical one-body vertices. The multiplicity check \
is fulfilled.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8895308415440407`*^9, 3.889530867561658*^9}, {
