Cell["\<\
Diagonally-and-antidiagonally-dressed disjoint Bogoliubov diagrams with three \
identical one-body vertices\
\>", "Subsection",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9123225301750393`*^9, 3.9123225545237913`*^9}, {
