Cell["\<\
There are only 207 inequivalent third-order disconnected diagrams with \
identical one-body vertex. The multiplicity check is fulfilled.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8895308415440407`*^9, 3.889530867561658*^9}, {
